_sText:
A small bomb/defuse map with two outside zones and four ways to go from one to another: one way under each tower, across the hole in the wall (if you climb thanks to the leaves) and a fourth one by climbing the ladder.
Over the starting spots there are a few places to cover for a sniper, if you like.

Please, vote it! I want to know your opinions ;-)

Made by [.EPICO.] Rikimaru TM
